            <h1>True <span>Beauty</span> Needs No Disguise </h1>
            <p>Beauty skin is a sign of healthy and well-cared skin.
             A good skincare routine helps keep the skin clean, soft, and glowing.
             Drinking enough water and eating healthy food also improves skin beauty.
             Using moisturizer and sunscreen daily protects the skin from dryness and sun damage. 
             Taking care of skin regularly makes you look fresh and confident.</p>
